{"tid":343691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶]G奶寫真女星的勾引大叔實驗 巨乳完全被看光光","createTime":"2017-08-01T16:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T01:29:10.000Z","uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ee8ed15c1adbc3ca12292ecb493c3be4229043","tid":343691,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ck101.com/thread-3433051-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-3433051-1-1.html&d=%2F1R3kjJOvyM4pFnsqpqDSozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c56d3806\" target=\"_blank\">https://ck101.com/thread-3433051-1-1.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/GophVaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FGophVaC.jpg&h=a67bccda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本的節目現在是沒有在分級了嗎？從前陣子開始就一直有電視節目播出超尺度的畫面！但我們當然是開心的接受啦～＞＞＞看個旅遊節目我竟然就in了？女神泡溫泉不經意露出好身材 浴巾完全包不住了啦..(54P)<br />\n＞＞＞日本節目好精彩！只是想看個過年特別節目 竟然看到F罩杯女星晃奶跟開高衩辣妹啊！(10P)<br />\n這次介紹的日本電視節目「芸能界煩悩CUP 有吉のドッキリ初笑い!」的主題就是巨乳女星進去混浴溫泉會被大叔們瞄幾次！主角就是圍著浴巾的日本22歲G奶寫真女優「和地つかさ」，測試對象是「小峠英二」和「上島竜兵」！這段內容被放到日本論壇上之後也引起了廣泛討論！影片後面還找來另一位歪果女生測試「武田修宏」，大家一起來看看吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/II8zEZK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FII8zEZK.gif&h=64444f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.imgs.cc/img/QbhiVFo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FQbhiVFo.gif&h=97f881a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.imgs.cc/img/LsNaY0c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FLsNaY0c.gif&h=46462415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我是來求原片的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1a03010417ae4bc9b7187d05ad0bf04c0f1121","tid":343691,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"屌，po錯台添"},{"pid":"f74ca69227d696f792a081f190f11ea69c94898a","tid":343691,"uid":124